reviewText: love anything that makes me laugh  afv is great
DID A GREAT JOB AND FAST SHIPPING
my favorite part are when the mom slides down the slide with her child and she gets to the end and hit the ground and you here a boing sound effect.

If you like the show AFHV, then you'll enjoy the bits on this tape. The big drawback is the sound and picture quality. The whole tape is like a home movie with the narration a little garbled. It is watchable and funny, but not as finished a product as you see on tv.
